# üöÄ Complete PWA Setup for Your Portfolio

I'll help you transform your existing portfolio into a **Progressive Web App (PWA)**. This will make your site installable, work offline, and provide a native app-like experience.

## üìÅ File Structure
```
your-portfolio/
‚îú‚îÄ‚îÄ index.html (your existing file)
‚îú‚îÄ‚îÄ site.webmanifest
‚îú‚îÄ‚îÄ sw.js (service worker)
‚îú‚îÄ‚îÄ offline.html
‚îú‚îÄ‚îÄ icons/
‚îÇ   ‚îú‚îÄ‚îÄ icon-72x72.png
‚îÇ   ‚îú‚îÄ‚îÄ icon-96x96.png
‚îÇ   ‚îú‚îÄ‚îÄ icon-128x128.png
‚îÇ   ‚îú‚îÄ‚îÄ icon-144x144.png
‚îÇ   ‚îú‚îÄ‚îÄ icon-152x152.png
‚îÇ   ‚îú‚îÄ‚îÄ icon-192x192.png
